title: Tennessee Gov. Bill Lee Issues 'Safer at Home' Executive Order for State
description: Tennessee Gov. Lee issued a "Safer at Home" executive order for the state in response to the coronavirus pandemic at a press conference.
content:
Tennessee Gov. Bill Lee issued a “Safer at Home” executive order for the entire state at a press conference in Nashville on Monday afternoon.
